venue_data.about_description: Faccia a Faccia is the new coastal Italian restaurant from award-winning chef and restaurateur Ken Oringer.
venue_data.need_to_know_description:
We reserve tables and bar seats. Please confirm when booking what you have selected. We will not be able to accommodate you at a table if you have booked bar seats. 

In order to accommodate all of our guests, we allot a maximum of two hours per reservation, regardless of party size, bar seating or table.

venue_data.about_description: The Painted Burro features an exciting seasonal menu that highlights the diverse cuisines of Latin America. From our wonderfully flavored moles, our selection of inspired tacos, to our extensive list of over 100 craft tequilas, the goal at The Painted Burro is to impart our local chef-driven styles into modern interpretations of Latin American cuisine with a strong respect for tradition.
venue_data.need_to_know_description:
LARGE PARTIES: We may have availability for larger groups! Please give us a call to inquire.
KITCHEN ADMIN FEE: There is a 5% Kitchen Admin Fee applied to all checks. We feel this is the most transparent & best way in lieu of raising our menu prices, to help close the gap in wage disparities between our Front of the House and Back of the House employees. Thank you for your support & understanding!
